      <guid>https://angebot.tole.es/b00005om2j-de-max-factor-lipfinity-lip-colour-lasts-up-to-24hr-.../</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Es gibt ein &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00005OM2J/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;MAX FACTOR - Lipfinity Lip Colour - Lasts up to 24hr - 2in1 Rich Colour  Transfer-proof  Long-lasting  Moisturising Lipstick - 180 Spiritual - 4.2g&lt;/a&gt; hier:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00005OM2J/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/41oxrWBgCyL._SL500_._SL400_.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;MAX FACTOR - Lipfinity Lip Colour - Lasts up to 24hr - 2in1 Rich Colour  Transfer-proof  Long-lasting  Moisturising Lipstick - 180 Spiritual - 4.2g&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ℹ️:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;RICH INGREDIENTS: This Lipfinity Lipstick is formulated with ingredients that ensure a smooth finish. The moisturising balm provides a lustrous shine, leaving your lips feeling soft and hydrated.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;SATIN FINISH: Offering a satin finish, this lipstick gives your lips a sophisticated look. Its longevity ensures that your lips stay perfect all day, making it an ideal choice for any occasion.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;MAX FACTOR BRAND: MAX FACTOR has a rich history in the beauty industry, known for creating the signature looks of Hollywoods Golden Age stars. Today, they continue to inspire with products designed to meet the needs of modern women.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CRUELTY-FREE: This Lipfinity Lipstick is cruelty-free, making it a responsible choice for beauty enthusiasts. It is suitable for different skin types, ensuring everyone can enjoy its benefits.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;LONG-LASTING LIP COLOUR: Immerse yourself in the world of vibrant lip colours with this Lipfinity Lipstick. A 2-in-1 lipstick balm, it offers a multi-dimensional colour and shine that last up to 24 hours.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B00005OM2J/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🛒 kauf es hier!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA